item.title: CVE-2023-5082|2024-08-02T07:44:53.677Z -- unknown -- history%20log%20by%20click5
item.description: The History Log by click5 WordPress plugin before 1.0.13 does not properly sanitise and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by admin users when using the Smash Balloon Social Photo Feed plugin alongside it.
